snippet.title: Super Mario Legend: NCFC 2010 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Legend is a new Mario fangame I'm working on. This is a small trailer for NCFC 2010, showing gameplay footage.

Song: My Skateboard Will Go On - Anamanaguchi
